metadata.name: Crimson Dawn
metadata.description:
Light breaks horizon
Day begins pink and crimson
Hosannas of joy.

Original photographic chemigram, digitally colored.  This piece is my first NFT of 2022 and represents the hope that each new day brings, particularly as we start a new year.

Licensed for non-commercial personal use.

3000x3000 pixels.

Full size high resolution file available to collector on request.

Wanda Oliver
Jan., 6, 2022
